<template>
  <v-container fluid>
    <v-row align="center">
      <v-col cols="6">
        <v-subheader>
          Appended icon
        </v-subheader>
      </v-col>
      <v-col  class="d-flex"
        cols="12"
        sm="6">
        <v-select
          v-model="e2"
          :items="states"
          append-outer-icon="mdi-plus"
          menu-props="auto"
          hide-details
          label="Select"
          single-line
        ></v-select>
      </v-col>
    </v-row>
  </v-container>
</template>


<script>
  export default {
    data () {
      return {
        e1: 'Florida',
        e2: 'Texas',
        e3: null,
        e4: null,
        states: [
          'Alabama', 'Wyoming',
        ],
      }
    },
  }
</script>
